trans-unit.source: It is possible to print each page of a document using different page settings.
trans-unit.target: Det er mulig å skrive ut alle sidene i et dokument med ulike sideinnstillinger.

trans-unit.source: You set page settings by modifying individual properties of the <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.QueryPageSettingsEventArgs.PageSettings%2A> property or by setting the property to a <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PageSettings>.
trans-unit.target: Du har angitt sideinnstillinger ved å endre enkelte egenskaper for det <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.QueryPageSettingsEventArgs.PageSettings%2A>egenskapen eller ved å sette egenskapen til en <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PageSettings>.</xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PageSettings> </xref:System.Drawing.Printing.QueryPageSettingsEventArgs.PageSettings%2A>

trans-unit.source: The print job can also be canceled by setting the <xref:System.ComponentModel.CancelEventArgs.Cancel%2A> property to `true`.
trans-unit.target: Du kan også avbryte utskriftsjobben ved å angi den <xref:System.ComponentModel.CancelEventArgs.Cancel%2A>egenskapen `true`.</xref:System.ComponentModel.CancelEventArgs.Cancel%2A>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Drawing.Printing.QueryPageSettingsEventArgs"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Drawing.Printing.QueryPageSettingsEventArgs"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: The page settings for the page to be printed.
Gets or sets the page settings for the page to be printed.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir innstillingene for siden for utskrift.
